  <section class="section bg-light" id="section-feedback">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
          <div class="section-title">
            <h3 class="title mb-4">Vi sao dieu nay quan trong: lang nghe nguoi dung chia se</h3>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-9 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="tiny-single-item text-center">
            <div class="tiny-slide client-testi text-center">
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">After adopting NocoBase, the time we spend on administrative tasks dropped by 50%, collaboration and communication improved, and our recruitment process became faster and more efficient.</p>
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">At TEDxDUTH, we believe innovation and collaboration can change the world. NocoBase helps us streamline daily operations so we can focus more energy on what truly matters: creating inspiring events and spreading meaningful ideas.</p>
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">If your organization is dealing with chaotic or inefficient workflows, NocoBase is not just a tool. It is a comprehensive solution that unlocks your team's potential and makes more possible. For us, NocoBase has been a true game changer: it has empowered us to dream bigger, transformed how we work, and continues to shape our community.</p>
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">We are grateful to NocoBase for being an indispensable partner on our journey. Together, we keep advancing innovation and the spread of ideas.</p>
              <img src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/20250713094749.png" class="mt-4 mb-4" width="160" alt="TED" />
              <h6 class="text-primary">Sarantis Antoniou <small class="text-muted">Lead Organizer </small></h6>
            </div>
            <div class="tiny-slide client-testi text-center">
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">We evaluated Airtable and NocoDB before ultimately choosing NocoBase because it better matched our needs for system flexibility and deployment control. We can deploy NocoBase in our AWS environment, it does not limit the number of users, its permission controls are fine-grained, and its separation of pages and data lets us customize the frontend flexibly. Built-in workflows and automatic API generation have also greatly improved efficiency.</p>
              <a rel="nofollow" href="https://classmethod.jp/" target="_blank"><img src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/20250713094650.png" class="mt-4 mb-4" width="160" alt="classmethod" /></a>
              <h6 class="text-primary">クラスメソッド株式会社（Classmethod, Inc.）</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="tiny-slide client-testi text-center">
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">Before choosing NocoBase, we did not have a dedicated customer service and operations management system. As the business grew quickly, we needed to build fast and support more and more demands, and NocoBase solved that well. Its relational data modeling is especially strong, allowing us to integrate different data structures efficiently so customer service staff can quickly look up user information and handle entitlement issues in real time, which has greatly improved operational efficiency.</p>
              <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.plaud.ai/" target="_blank"><img src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/20250713094635.png" class="mt-4 mb-4" width="160" alt="PLAUD" /></a>
              <h6 class="text-primary">PLAUD Product Manager Lucas</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="tiny-slide client-testi text-center">
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">We had been looking for a flexible no-code platform to build a fully customized scheduling system for our client Okechamp and its rapidly growing logistics business. During our evaluation, NocoBase stood out for its schema-first architecture, modular design, and active community. It made it easy for us to implement custom views and report management, and we plan to keep using NocoBase in more client projects.</p>
              <img src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/20250713094700.png" class="mt-4 mb-4" width="160" alt="Lukardi" />
              <h6 class="text-primary">Lukardi SA</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="tiny-slide client-testi text-center">
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">We used to rely on paper-based processes for HR management and leave approvals, which was inefficient and error-prone. After building HR, attendance, leave, and related processes with NocoBase, we achieved truly paperless operations, and managing more than 110 employees became far more efficient and intuitive. NocoBase's flexible interface design and powerful APIs fully meet the diverse needs of our real estate business. Compared with tools like Salesforce, it is not only highly customizable but also available through a one-time purchase model, making it extremely cost-effective. We are now planning to migrate more systems to NocoBase, including CRM, and make it the company portal and core business platform.</p>
              <a rel="nofollow" href="https://housewell-group.jp/" target="_blank"><img src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/20250713094720.png" class="mt-4 mb-4" width="160" alt="HouseWell" /></a>
              <h6 class="text-primary">ハウスウェル株式会社(HouseWell)</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="tiny-slide client-testi text-center">
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">When building our smart factory system, we chose NocoBase as the core platform. Its streamlined configuration process allows non-technical staff to build system pages quickly, greatly improving development efficiency. At the same time, its plugin ecosystem and workflow engine help us adapt flexibly to a variety of business scenarios while maintaining system quality and scalability. With NocoBase's fine-grained permission system, we achieved efficient collaboration and strong data security across processes such as equipment maintenance and HR management. After deployment, together with a PC, mobile, and 5G architecture, it enabled real-time data feedback and efficient data entry, laying a solid foundation for our smart factory initiative.</p>
              <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.bielcrystal.com" target="_blank"><img src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/20250713094732.png" class="mt-4 mb-4" width="160" alt="BIEL" /></a>
              <h6 class="text-primary">BIEL Crystal Holdings Limited</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="tiny-slide client-testi text-center">
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">Among many modern database products, NocoBase is the only solution that truly made me feel we could have it all. We needed a non-SaaS, low-code, extensible system to support collaboration across dozens of teams and highly standardized professional scenarios. The learning curve was unexpectedly smooth. Within just a few days, I was able to build business processes without depending on developers.</p>
              <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.aoya-hk.com/" target="_blank"><img src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/20250713094804.png" class="mt-4 mb-4" width="160" alt="奥雅设计" /></a>
              <h6 class="text-primary">Aoya Design, Business Lead Zhang Tingyuan</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="tiny-slide client-testi text-center">
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">After comparing and evaluating several low-code platforms from China and abroad, we ultimately chose NocoBase. It supports local deployment and functional extensibility, which perfectly matches our high standards for data security and system customization in the chemistry field. NocoBase's professional support team and flexible data modeling capabilities made our go-live process efficient and reliable.</p>
              <a rel="nofollow" href="https://xtalpi.com/" target="_blank"><img src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/20250713094812.png" class="mt-4 mb-4" width="160" alt="晶泰科技" /></a>
              <h6 class="text-primary">XtalPi Project Lead Xiong Zhi</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="tiny-slide client-testi text-center">
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">I cannot emphasize enough the great experience we've had with NocoBase as a no-code/low-code platform. It stands out as exceptionally user-friendly, making our development process both smooth and efficient. What impressed me most was how easy it was to work on development of the user experience once the data model was in place. This streamlined approach allowed us to develop a full-fledged system, designed to be used by several hundred organizations, in just a matter of weeks.</p>
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">NocoBase has effectively shattered the common misconception that powerful systems require months or even years of work. I highly recommend it for any organization looking to fast-track their development cycle without sacrificing quality.</p>
              <a rel="nofollow" href="https://sambruk.se/" target="_blank"><img src="https://static-docs.nocobase.com/20250713094827.png" class="mt-4 mb-4" width="160" alt="Sambruk" /></a>
              <h6 class="text-primary">Thomas Wennersten <small class="text-muted">CTO</small></h6>
            </div>
            <div class="tiny-slide client-testi text-center">
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">NocoBase serves as the core for data management, API services, and workflows, greatly reducing development complexity and allowing our developers to focus more on implementing business logic, which has significantly improved development efficiency.</p>
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">NocoBase offers excellent integration capabilities, connecting seamlessly with various third-party services and systems to enable data sharing and functional integration. That means we do not need to build everything from scratch. Instead, we can make full use of existing services and resources and quickly integrate them into our applications. This not only reduces development time and cost, but also makes our applications richer and more capable in meeting diverse user needs.</p>
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">In this fast-moving digital era, NocoBase is undoubtedly a powerful tool for helping us meet challenges and drive innovation. Thanks to the NocoBase team for all their work.</p>
              <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.chinaunicom.com/" target="_blank"><img src="https://nocobase-docs.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/liantong.png" class="mt-4 mb-4" width="160" alt="" /></a>
              <h6 class="text-primary">Xinjiang Unicom Innovation Lab</h6>
            </div>
          </div><!--end owl carousel-->
